msgid "Glass panes are thin layers of glass which neatly connect to their neighbors as you build them."
msgstr ""
"Los paneles de vidrio son capas delgadas de vidrio que se conectan "
"perfectamente a otros paneles de vidrio a medida que los colocas."

msgid "Stained glass panes are thin layers of stained glass which neatly connect to their neighbors as you build them. They come in many different colors."
msgstr ""
"Los paneles de vidrio son capas delgadas de vidrio que se conectan "
"perfectamente a otros vidiros a medida que los colocas. Vienen en muchos "
"colores diferentes."

msgid "Stained Glass Pane"
msgstr "Panel de vidrio tintado"

msgid "Iron Bars"
msgstr "Barrotes de hierro"

msgid "Iron bars neatly connect to their neighbors as you build them."
msgstr "Los barrotes de hierro se conectan perfectamente a sus vecinos a medida que los construyes."

msgid "Glass Pane"
msgstr "Panel de vidrio"

msgid "@1 Glass Pane"
msgstr "Panel de vidrio teñido de @1"
